<span class="nt">div</span> <span class="nt">p</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="nl">color</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="no">red</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="p">}</span>

<span class="c">/* ìì‹ ì…€ë ‰í„° (Child Combinator)
